title: Indonesia ends search for victims of school collapse with at least 61 dead
summary: A search for the bodies of victims from a school collapse in Indonesia has called off after the death toll finalised.
key_points: A search for the bodies of victims from a school collapse in Indonesia has called off after the death toll finalised.
The death toll in the Indonesian school collapse has risen to at least 61 dead.
